					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Super Mario Bros. has four tables to translate metatiles to hardware tile numbers: one for metatiles $00-$3F, one for $40-$7F, one for $80-$BF, and one for $C0-$FF. The upper 2 bits select both which table is used and which attribute is used.</div>

