						<div class="postbody">So it seems it could be a case per case thing.  My goal for my editor is that it could be used for making more than one game so I try to be make it as generic as possible.
<br />
<br />So I will have to rethink a few things regarding my data model, to be able to make metatile out of metatile and how to handle background attribute properly.  It still in it's early stage (I can only put 1 hour once in a while on it) so I can still change what it will do and how.
<br />
<br />If people have any comment about what they would like to have as a feature if they had their own editors, I'm all ears.  Other people comment will make me see things that I may have missed and could need later myself .</div>

